      "acceptanceCriteria": "The mathematical model form, including turbulence closure and hemolysis power-law model, must be justified relative to the physics of the COU.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model is selected based on published literature for rotating machinery hemolysis predictions. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model is the standard for this device class and is appropriate for the shear stress magnitudes encountered."
